# ----- Data + caches -----
# Cached Statcast pulls are organized into data/<year>/ subfolders.
# Prior-season folders are immutable and committed to the repo so codespaces
# start warm. The current-season folder rolls forward daily and is ignored.
# Update this line at the start of each new MLB season.
data/2026/

# pybaseball http cache
.pybaseball/

# ----- Generated reports -----
# Single-matchup outputs (regenerable)
*_matchup.md
*_matchup.html

# Lineup outputs
lineup_*.md
lineup_*.html

# Per-player summary scratch outputs (regenerable)
*_summary.md
*_pitcher_summary.md

